Program: Great Lives
Title: Field Marshal Bill Slim
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00dhb1n
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 10 Mar 2017
Series of biographical discussions with Matthew Parris. General Sir Mike Jackson, former Head of the British Army, nominates Field Marshal Bill Slim, leader of the Burma Campaign. Military historian Julian Thompson lends weight to the argument that Slim, less well known today than other Second World War Generals, was perhaps the greatest commander of the 20th century. Show less